NPCDialogue.LocalizedString: MOONBEARD! HOW LOVELY TO SEE YOU AGAIN! @VIOLET, THRASH, PIP... I'M SO HAPPY YOU CAME. @AND JOT... AS ALWAYS... THIS LAND IS INDEBTED TO YOUR BRAVERY AND HEROISM. @THANK YOU FOR ALL THAT YOU HAVE DONE. @MOONBEARD, WHAT CAN YOU TELL ME OF THIS LATEST KERFUFFLE? @IT'S THAT MISCHIEVOUS HUMGRUMP AGAIN, ISN'T IT?

INDEED IT IS, YOUR HIGHNESS. #WITH SOME NEW GREASY TRICKS. @HE HAS A NEW KIND OF METAMAGIC THAT CAN ALLOW PASSAGE IN AND OUT OF OUR BOOK. @HUMGRUMP MAY USE THIS MAGIC TO GAIN POWER OVER OUR LAND. @HE COULD CHANGE THE STORY OF OUR BOOK... FOR THE WORSE! @IF THE STORY GETS WORSE, OUR BOOK COULD BE... PUT AWAY, ON THE SHELF. @IF THAT HAPPENED, THE LIFE FORCE OF THIS LAND WOULD BE UTTERLY DIMINISHED.
THE STORY OF OUR LIVES WOULD BE FROZEN FOREVER IN A MOST MISERABLE WAY. @WE CANNOT ALLOW THIS TO HAPPEN!
